PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 783 revoking the maximum residue limits (MRLs) for demeton (Systox), an organo-phosphorus insecticide which has been used on a range of food crops including potatoes, beans, grapefruit, strawberries and almonds.
